points_raised:
- adigital:
- presented their association (the voice of 500 Spanish technology and digital economy businesses) and its main activities;
- explained the nature and purpose of the Certificate for Algorithmic Transparency, created to support the implementation of the AI Act;
- reported on the implementation of “lAméricas”, a project focused on integrating AI into the processes of Latin American companies;
- announced the creation of a dispute resolution system for the Digital Services Act;
- announced a repository on companies’ suggestions for the digital Omnibus package. The Commission representatives thanked adigital for the information provided.

