omnibus and", "function": null}, {"name": "underlined the importance of avoiding overlaps in consumer regulations and", "function": null}, {"name": "fostering simplification.", "function": null}, {"name": "The Commission representatives took note of the comments made by", "function": null}, {"name": "Skyscanner.", "function": null}, {"name": "Conclusions: N/A", "function": null}]}

